{"tid":803214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網友訂制家具要求「雕成龍的頭」 結果•••","createTime":"2018-09-02T05:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T09:48:30.000Z","uid":32938,"like":3166,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"1851fd31247a9a2fb9e44932060144b6844668aa","tid":803214,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"【橙訊】9月2號，一則關於「雕成龍的頭」的微博引發網友們的熱議，網友看圖後紛紛哭笑不得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/134304_0f88ab4505bae55a3b9c54fb3eb0fac1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F134304_0f88ab4505bae55a3b9c54fb3eb0fac1.png&h=bd15c224&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/134305_0f88ab4505bae55a3b9c54fb3eb0fac1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F134305_0f88ab4505bae55a3b9c54fb3eb0fac1.png&h=55025285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國內一個網友定制了一套傢俱，當傢俱初步成型之後，客戶不是太滿意，於是通過社交程式告知廠商家具需要修改，需求把家具兩端雕成龍的頭，寓意鴻運當頭的意思，於是雕刻師傅毫無疑問的開始動工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/134330_9d726398f600010713e48b3475827f01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F134330_9d726398f600010713e48b3475827f01.png&h=d3cde3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待完工後，客戶收到成品出現成龍的雕刻頭像，方驚覺廠家把「龍頭」理解錯誤，不得不感慨中國文字博大精深，雕成「龍」的頭，還是雕「成龍」的頭，於是將事件上載到朋友圈，網友則讚揚廠家師傅的雕刻技術高超，效果堪比蠟像。"},{"pid":"2fc93be1732d5e923e12f221f6c651fd174e2252","tid":803214,"uid":203037,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1365efe900b6ee63a506b5ec55b300101b17cb","tid":803214,"uid":30794,"like":1119,"dislike":1,"score":1118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"我仲諗緊有咩人咁鍾意成龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8309e6a21dba971e35fa7bd3bcbb813ce30440","tid":803214,"uid":43966,"like":716,"dislike":4,"score":712,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"咩原因會雕個仆街既頭落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b5c2061a687ae25fd8df3823abf6c2899f297d","tid":803214,"uid":56401,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"3e95174a9ae1cf97c994244e69da2b77f04ce30e","tid":803214,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d8a8f6709681939d525a4e9f6ab7240dc3cb36","tid":803214,"uid":2419,"like":753,"dislike":1,"score":752,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://24.p3k.hu/app/uploads/2013/11/jackie-chan-mem3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F24.p3k.hu%2Fapp%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F11%2Fjackie-chan-mem3.jpg&h=09414333&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5376ce7fa6344a95d3b1aedb70446f89a10392c","tid":803214,"uid":887,"like":583,"dislike":1,"score":582,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"但係又雕得幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f9d7d866f3c2761456db19657e31da87ba5d71","tid":803214,"uid":59664,"like":28,"dislike":74,"score":-46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:52:12.000Z","msg":"下雨天留客天留我不留個fd"},{"pid":"fff419648224fad115a408cb9ce45bce6de3d81c","tid":803214,"uid":20473,"like":210,"dislike":6,"score":204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"龍係皇帝先用得 真係雕條龍唔怕俾人殺頭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face