":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"仆街, 成龍個頭都雕到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e048d4d6e2283ced07bb1546685ccbbf6e61d42","tid":803214,"uid":23468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"我屌，好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339b696607325ae2091daf4608b55655d4265d81","tid":803214,"uid":194781,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"厲害了 我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a611f5c11952a7e8f577598814ee09fa7f08e1e4","tid":803214,"uid":92467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"成龍條柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為雕咗條撚出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca66c094916015fa2fd38cfd32f13c4606d26bf7","tid":803214,"uid":70501,"like":84,"dislike":5,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A9%99%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A9%2599%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E&d=nP0iKoujsGWWgNThry21MP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6c39bc94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A9%99%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n橙新聞是香港一個親建制派的網絡媒體。<br />\n公司背景<br />\n<br />\n《<span style=\"color: orange;\">橙新聞</span>》由雲通科技有限公司於2014年創立。雲通科技有限公司<sp